 class="vds-font-headline-xs word-break" data-heading-size="xs" data-heading-bold="false" data-test="text">Roof windows</h3></span><div class="prose text-velux-grey-800"><div class="word-break vds-font-body-m text-velux-grey-800" data-test="body-text">VELUX roof windows let in both light and life. Whether you're converting loft, adding an extension, or simply brightening up a room, our diverse collections are designed to transform your space with natural light and fresh air.</div></div><!----><!----></div><!----><!----><span><!--[--><!--[--><a data-component="CompButton" href="/products/roof-windows" target class="inline-flex items-center justify-center transition-colors duration-300 cursor-pointer aria-disabled:pointer-events-none aria-disabled:cursor-default vds-font-button-xs text-velux-button-tertiary-initial [@media(hover:hover)]:hover:text-velux-button-tertiary-hover aria-disabled:text-velux-button-tertiary-disabled gap-1" data-variant="link" aria-label="Learn more" data-v-4df87841><!--[--><!----><span class="" data-v-4df87841>Learn more</span><svg class="w-2 h-2 shrink-0" aria-hidden="true" data-test="icon-trailing" data-v-4df87841><!----><use xlink:href="/dist/velux-marketing/client/icon-sprite-bb622257bf7cf195-4de1d8d4.svg#direction-chevron-right-16"></use></svg><!--]--></a><!----><!----><!--]--><!--]--></span></div></article><!--]--></div><div class="card-slider-item" data-v-8cc73ffb><!--[--><article class="flex flex-col justify-between w-full word-break gap-6" data-card-index="1"><div class="relative"><!----><a class="cursor-pointer" href="/products/solar-and-electric-solutions" target><!--[--><!----><!--]--><!----></a></div><div class="flex flex-col justify-start gap-4 pb-6 h-full"><div class="grid gap-2 sm:gap-4"><!----><span><h3 class="vds-font-headline-xs word-break" data-heading-size="xs" data-heading-bold="false" data-test="text">Solar and electric solutions</h3></span><div class="prose text-velux-grey-800"><div class="word-break vds-font-body-m text-velux-grey-800" data-test="body-text">VELUX solar and electric solutions make it easier to control the level of light in your home and shield it from the heat. With nothing more than a click, you can ensure the optimal levels with our powered woof windows, shutters and blinds.
</div></div><!----><!----></div><!----><!----><span><!--[--><!--[--><a data-component="CompButton" href="/products/solar-and-electric-solutions" target class="inline-flex items-center justify-center transition-colors duration-300 cursor-pointer aria-disabled:pointer-events-none aria-disabled:cursor-default vds-font-button-xs text-velux-button-tertiary-initial [@media(hover:hover)]:hover:text-velux-button-tertiary-hover aria-disabled:text-velux-button-tertiary-disabled gap-1" data-variant="link" aria-label="Learn more" data-v-4df87841><!--[--><!----><span class="" data-v-4df87841>Learn more</span><svg class="w-2 h-2 shrink-0" aria-hidden="true" data-test="icon-trailing" data-v-4df87841><!----><use xlink:href="/dist/velux-marketing/client/icon-sprite-bb622257bf7cf195-4de1d8d4.svg#direction-chevron-right-16"></use></svg><!--]--></a><!----><!----><!--]--><!--]--></span></div></article><!--]--></div><div class="card-slider-item" data-v-8cc73ffb><!--[--><article class="flex flex-col justify-between w-full word-break gap-6" data-card-index="2"><div class="relative"><!----><a class="cursor-pointer" href="/products/flat-roof-windows" target><!--[--><!----><!--]--><!----></a></div><div class="flex flex-col justify-start gap-4 pb-6 h-full"><div class="grid gap-2 sm:gap-4"><!----><span><h3 class="vds-font-headline-xs word-break" data-heading-size="xs" data-heading-bold="false" data-test="text">Flat roof windows</h3></span><div class="prose text-velux-grey-800"><div class="word-break vds-font-body-m text-velux-grey-800" data-test="body-text">VELUX flat roof windows are the ideal way to bring more natural light and fresh air into spaces with flat or low-pitched roofs. Future-proof your home with innovative skylights that create brighter, healthier and more energy-efficient environments.</div></div><!----><!----></div><!----><!----><span><!--[--><!--[--><a data-component="CompButton" href="/products/flat-roof-windows" target class="inline-flex items-center justify-center transitio