</div></div><!----><!----></div><!----><!----><span><!--[--><!--[--><a data-component="CompButton" href="/products/blinds-and-shutters" target class="inline-flex items-center justify-center transition-colors duration-300 cursor-pointer aria-disabled:pointer-events-none aria-disabled:cursor-default vds-font-button-xs text-velux-button-tertiary-initial [@media(hover:hover)]:hover:text-velux-button-tertiary-hover aria-disabled:text-velux-button-tertiary-disabled gap-1" data-variant="link" aria-label="Learn more" data-v-4df87841><!--[--><!----><span class="" data-v-4df87841>Learn more</span><svg class="w-2 h-2 shrink-0" aria-hidden="true" data-test="icon-trailing" data-v-4df87841><!----><use xlink:href="/dist/velux-marketing/client/icon-sprite-bb622257bf7cf195-4de1d8d4.svg#direction-chevron-right-16"></use></svg><!--]--></a><!----><!----><!--]--><!--]--></span></div></article><!--]--></div><div class="card-slider-item" data-v-8cc73ffb><!--[--><article class="flex flex-col justify-between w-full word-break gap-6" data-card-index="4"><div class="relative"><!----><a class="cursor-pointer" href="/products/sun-tunnels" target><!--[--><!----><!--]--><!----></a></div><div class="flex flex-col justify-start gap-4 pb-6 h-full"><div class="grid gap-2 sm:gap-4"><!----><span><h3 class="vds-font-headline-xs word-break" data-heading-size="xs" data-heading-bold="false" data-test="text">Sun tunnels</h3></span><div class="prose text-velux-grey-800"><div class="word-break vds-font-body-m text-velux-grey-800" data-test="body-text"><p>Transform dark spaces into bright, inviting areas with VELUX sun tunnels. Our innovative light tubes are the perfect solution for bringing natural daylight into every corner of your home, even where traditional windows can't reach.</p></div></div><!----><!----></div><!----><!----><span><!--[--><!--[--><a data-component="CompButton" href="/products/sun-tunnels" target class="inline-flex items-center justify-center transition-colors duration-300 cursor-pointer 