ea6053","componentName":"CardSliderDDS","dataSource":"{ACBDF4C3-793E-4EC2-B052-BEA8B2AEB8A1}","params":{"Variant":"{262745B0-DB4A-4CD9-86A3-F35EEAA3FD05}","cardAspectRatio":"{86E14879-F45D-4844-B607-C92065245EEC}","VariantValue":"story","cardAspectRatioValue":"1\u002F1"},"fields":{"headline":"Discover a wide range of products","cards":[{"badge":null,"drawer":"","title":"Roof windows","description":"VELUX roof windows let in both light and life. Whether you're converting loft, adding an extension, or simply brightening up a room, our diverse collections are designed to transform your space with natural light and fresh air.","link":{"href":"\u002Fproducts\u002Froof-windows","text":"","linkType":"internal","target":""},"linkText":"Learn more","media":{"lightbox":false,"caption":null,"mediaItems":[{"alt":"Attic living room with sloped ceiling and large VELUX roof windows.","credit":"","caption":"","isVideo":false,"isEmbedded":false,"video":null,"size":"44.3 MB","src":"https:\u002F\u002Fcontenthub.velux.com\u002Fapi\u002Fpublic\u002Fcontent\u002Ff7e11-b30e1-364fb_Master?v=bdf880a1"}]}},{"badge":null,"drawer":"","title":"Solar and electric solutions","description":"VELUX solar and electric solutions make it easier to control the level of light in your home and shield it from the heat. With nothing more than a click, you can ensure the optimal levels with our powered woof windows, shutters and blinds.\n","link":{"href":"\u002Fproducts\u002Fsolar-and-electric-solutions","text":"","linkType":"internal","target":""},"linkText":"Learn more","media":{"lightbox":false,"caption":null,"mediaItems":[{"alt":"Attic bedroom with sloped ceiling and VELUX roof windows, natural light entering.","credit":"","caption":"","isVideo":false,"isEmbedded":false,"video":null,"size":"62.73 MB","src":"https:\u002F\u002Fcontenthub.velux.com\u002Fapi\u002Fpublic\u002Fcontent\u002Fce3f4-80a81-f44f6_Master?v=c13432c6"}]}},{"badge":null,"drawer":"","title":"Flat roof windows","description":"VELUX flat roof windows are the ideal way to bring more natural light and fresh air into spaces with flat or low-pitched roofs. Future-proof your home with innovative skylights that create brighter, healthier and more energy-efficient environments.","link":{"href":"\u002Fproducts\u002Fflat-roof-windows","text":"","linkType":"internal","target":""},"linkText":"Learn more","media":{"lightbox":false,"caption":null,"mediaItems":[{"alt":"Home office with VELUX roof window and large windows, natural light entering.","credit":"","caption":"","isVideo":false,"isEmbedded":false,"video":null,"size":"63.19 MB","src":"https:\u002F\u002Fcontenthub.velux.com\u002Fapi\u002Fpublic\u002Fcontent\u002Fcefcd-d8721-3747e_Master?v=f311f6b0"}]}},{"badge":null,"drawer":"","title":"Blinds and shutters","description":"VELUX blinds and shutters set the scene for daytime living and restful nights. From light dimming to complete darkness, our wide range of innovative blinds is designed to meet your every need - whether you're working, relaxing or tucking the kids to bed.\n","link":{"href":"\u002Fproducts\u002Fblinds-and-shutters","text":"","linkType":"internal","target":""},"linkText":"Learn more","media":{"lightbox":false,"caption":null,"mediaItems":[{"alt":"Attic kids room with sloped ceiling and VELUX roof window, filled with light.","credit":"","caption":"","isVideo":false,"isEmbedded":false,"video":null,"size":"82.76 MB","src":"https:\u002F\u002Fcontenthub.velux.com\u002Fapi\u002Fpublic\u002Fcontent\u002F75f8f-332b4-9e4d7_Master?v=13c263ee"}]}},{"badge":null,"drawer":"","title":"Sun tunnels","description":"\u003Cp\u003ETransform dark spaces into bright, inviting areas with VELUX sun tunnels. Our innovative light tubes are the perfect solution for bringing natural daylight into every corner of your home, even where traditional windows can't reach.\u003C\u002Fp\u003E","link":{"href":"\u002Fproducts\u002Fsun-tunnels","text":"","linkType":"internal","target":""},"linkText":"Learn more","media":{"lightbox":false,"caption":null,"mediaItems":[{"alt":"122592-01-XXL.tif","credit":"","caption":"","isVideo":false,"isEmbedded":false,"video":null,"size":"109.71 MB","src":"https:\u002F\u002Fcontenthub.velux.com\u002Fapi\u002Fpublic\u002Fcontent\u002F50f46-afeb7-5a44d_1x1?v=55c6869e&t=w960"}]}}]},"datasourceHasLanguageVersion":"true"},{"uid":"671570bb-ff75-481d-a1ea-02d64f808431","componentName":"DaylightEffectDDS","dataSource":"{B8C00DA4-A689-4059-A9C4-56EB90C0B13C}","params":{"variant":"Light"},"fields":{"cards":[{"title":{"value":"See how daylight transforms the room"},"text":{"value":""},"link":{"value":{"href":"\u002Fmagazine","text":"","anchor":"","linktype":"internal","class":"","title":"","target":"","querystring":"","id":"{E7BF279A-A2B2-483D-94BD-7726863D00DE}"}},"linkText":{"value":"Discover the benefits of daylight"},"id":"fd3312b3-ec9e-4d53-a25e-cd65cc73407e","name":"Daylight Effect Card 1","template":"Daylight Effect Card","media":{"lightbox":false,"mediaItems":[{"alt":"Schlafzimmer im Dachgeschoss mit schräger Decke und VELUX Dachfenster, durch das natürliches Licht einfällt.","credit":"","caption":"","isVideo":false,"isEmbedded":false,"video":null,"size":"7.07 MB","src":"https:\u002F\u002Fcontenthub.velux.com\u002Fapi\u002Fpublic\u002Fcontent\u002F44617-15f82-bf4b0_1x1?v=be6be486&t=w1440"}]}},{"title":{"value":"See how daylight transforms the room"},"text":{"value":""},"link":{"value":{"href":"\u002Fmagazine","text":"","anchor":"","linktype":"internal","class":"","title":"","target":"","querystring":"","id":"{E7BF279A-A2B2-483D-94BD-7726863D00DE}"}},"linkText":{"value":"Discover the benefits of daylight"},"id":"0e8ab7ba-70ab-4a14-a8db-9f2e1ee67ac5","name":"Daylight Effect Card 2","template":"Daylight Effect Card","media":{"lightbox":false,"mediaItems":[{"alt":"Schlafzimmer im Dachgeschoss mit schräger Decke und VELUX Dachfenstern, durch die natürliches Licht einfällt.","credit":"","caption":"","isVideo":false,"isEmbedded":false,"video":null,"size":"6.82 MB","src":"https:\u002F\u002Fcontenthub.velux.com\u002Fapi\u002Fpublic\u002Fcontent\u002Fd759d-d8f74-5c4e0_1x1?v=3fd55a3b&t=w1440"}]}},{"title":{"value":"See how daylight transforms the room"},"text":{"value":""},"link":{"value":{"href":"\u002Fmagazine","text":"","anchor":"","linktype":"internal","class":"","title":"","target":"","querystring":"","id":"{E7BF279A-A2B2-483D-94BD-7726863D00DE}"}},"linkText":{"value":"Discover the benefits of daylight"},"id":"2735d065-d416-4c0f-a5fc-00990d15e3f7","name":"Daylight Effect Card 3","template":"Daylight Effect Card","media":{"lightbox":false,"mediaItems":[{"alt":"Dachzimmer mit schräger Decke und drei großen VELUX Dachfenstern.","credit":"","caption":"","isVideo":false,"isEmbedded":false,"video":null,"size":"6.33 MB","src":"https:\u002F\u002Fcontenthub.velux.com\u002Fapi\u002Fpublic\u002Fcontent\u002Ffdd89-fc3ba-7a473_1x1?v=1b479031&t=w1440"}]}}]},"datasourceHasLanguageVersion":"true"},{"uid":"cab57c3d-fbd1-496c-8be3-a366903bc68a","componentName":"PromotedArticles","dataSource":"{399B15FE-7A4D-4539-843D-7DFF516B873B}","params":{},"fields":{"title":{"value":"Daylight and Spaces: the journal"},"articles":[{"title":{"value":"The best roof window solutions for a home extension"},"mainImage":{"value":{"src":"\u002F\u002Fafd-mv2.velux.com\u002F-\u002Fmedia\u002Fstories\u002Fgbi\u002Fhow-to-create-sun-drenched-family-friendly-spaces\u002Fhow-to-create-sun-drenched-family-friendly-spaces001.png?h=853&iar=0&w=1280&hash=4C585BE84C49402CA9F2E95FAEF6198E","alt":"Dining room with lots of plants a lot of sunshine coming through windows","width":"1280","height":"853"}},"introText":{"value":"Home extensions can be big or small. No matter the size, a home extension can provide more light and space for your house. Maybe you dream of seeing more of your garden each day. Or perhaps you want a conservatory where you can sit and enjoy the long summer nights. Whatever you may have in mind for your home extension, we have roof windows that can provide you with daylight, ventilation, and ambience.  "},"link":{"value":{"href":"\u002Fmagazine\u002Fbest-roof-windows-for-home-extensions","linktype":"internal"}},"id":"80dd257e-e36f-449a-a919-b60dcdcd0845","name":"68-the-top-roof-window-solutions-for-a-home-extension","template":"Article"},{"title":{"value":"The costs of replacing a roof window - how to budget for your replacement project"},"mainImage":{"value":{"thumbnailsrc":"https:\u002F\u002Fcontenthub.velux.com\u002Fapi\u002Fgateway\u002F362051\u002Fthumbnail","damid":"ID10125220","src":"https:\u002F\u002Fcontenthub.velux.com\u002Fapi\u002Fpublic\u002Fcontent\u002F87efa-d13b8-a1421_Master?v=a043cd9e&t=w960","damcontenttype":"Image","alt":"Attic home office with sloped ceiling and VELUX roof window, natural light.","stylelabsfilesize":"74.4"}},"introText":{"value":"Have you put off replacing your roof windows because it seems like a considerable extra cost? Then read on! Replacing your roof windows is neither as expensive nor as time-consuming as you may think. It all comes down to planning the process and budgeting. Here's all you need to know about the cost of replacing your roof windows. "},"link":{"value":{"href":"\u002Fmagazine\u002Fcosts-of-replacing-a-window","linktype":"internal"}},"id":"c6e59ea7-fff1-4c45-ab3e-e20add9ff919","name":"49-how-much-should-you-budget-for-replacement","template":"Article"},{"title":{"value":"How to cool down a room: seven strategies to keep your home cool throughout the summer"},"mainImage":{"value":{"damid":"cCPfl9Ui40qdYHA0FRGg3g","damcontenttype":"Image","stylelabsfilesize":"12.1","src":"https:\u002F\u002Fcontenthub.velux.com\u002Fapi\u002Fpublic\u002Fcontent\u002F6db37-fe795-9e4ff_Master?v=f292f3bf&t=w960","thumbnailsrc":"https:\u002F\u002Fcontenthub.velux.com\u002Fapi\u002Fgateway\u002F4646118\u002Fthumbnail"}},"introText":{"value":"The UK climate is changing; data from the Met Office shows that our summers are getting hotter. While you may rejoice in having more time for barbecues and visits to the seaside, no one likes to return home to a hot house. So, follow these seven tips to keep your home cool on even the hottest days, without having fans whirring 24 hours or installing air conditioning. "},"link":{"value":{"href":"\u002Fmagazine\u002Ftips-for-cooling-a-room","linktype":"internal"}},"id":"d64a75e5-9643-41a1-93a8-189af1079f3b","name":"156-how-to-cool-down-a-room","template":"Article"},{"title":{"value":"The VELUX Energy Guide"},"mainImage":{"value":{"src":"\u002F\u002Fafd-mv2.velux.com\u002F-\u002Fmedia\u002Farticles\u002Fgbi\u002Fenergy-efficiency\u002Fwinter.jpg?h=1280&iar=0&w=1920&hash=D236EC616416D82335ACFA1CB23ACC81","alt":"bedroom with a 2 in1 velux window","width":"1920","height":"1280"}},"introText":{"value":"VELUX has a long history of transforming indoor spaces with natural light and fresh air. With a focus on sustainability, improving energy efficiency in our homes remains essential. Roof windows are an effective solution to help reduce energy consumption for heating, cooling, and lighting."},"link":{"value":{"href":"\u002Fmagazine\u002Fvelux-energy-guide","linktype":"internal"}},"id":"4bcb84da-4072-4b05-a88b-fa25f0f9d506","name":"velux-energy-guide","template":"Article"}]},"datasourceHasLanguageVersion":"true"},{"uid":"46cb26e8-7c47-4115-ae72-d4a56d0d551c","componentName":"HeaderBlockVDS","dataSource":"{BFC26E60-7E14-45C9-B9FE-CCF262C11F0F}","params":{"layout":"{F6C96972-A389-4165-9B2A-9B2A636EB112}","tag":"{DF0CCBE5-1C9D-4106-A6C9-DBAD1564FD21}","layoutValue":"horizontal","tagValue":"h2"},"fields":{"title":{"value":"How can we help you?"},"description":{"value":""},"id":"bfc26e60-7e14-45c9-b9fe-ccf262c11f0f","name":"Header Block VDS - how can we help","template":"Header Block VDS"},"datasourceHasLanguageVersion":"true"},{"uid":"f61797f9-a715-4b27-a1aa-61cc7f69f892","componentName":"QuickLinksBlockVDS","dataSource":"{965C9EEE-2613-453C-81C1-3E7AE287F2AD}","params":{"maxLinksPerTile":"2","tileSize":"extra-large","columnCou